        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>faux finishing [300138843], painting techniques for special effects [300053380], painting techniques [300053343], painting and painting techniques [300149157], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
